channel.title: RsCalifornia 667/722 ~
channel.description:
[center] Currently working on a RsCalifornia as its hit: Alpha
Our great development team had been put under alot of presure as we fixed [b]ALOT[/b] of client & server sided hicks. RsCalifornia client is at optimum perfection with the lag and memory leaks fixed + increased login cycle running on [b]port: 8766[/b] as this keeps this has been known to increase connection between client+host.
Our primary goal is to ensure that the game-play resembles accurately as possible to RuneScape's gameplay. At this point we will be working on updating the current game-frame (not hard :P) to resemble current RS.
[b]Combat[/b] - Perfect maxhit formulas (All max hits are perfected for every weapon including ranged bows) - Double vengeance glitch has been fixed. - Poisoning (Anti-poisons work too, effects n stuff depending on each pot) - Mage stacking with melee has been fixed - Perfect switching as this had a majour part with our client response time.
[b]Server[/b] As some people know most 667 servers are at a high risk of 'dos' attacks. We limited 1 IP spam so any connection at a mass spam rate (which would normally be a dos attack) will be cycled and blocked by a filter we added. This does effect player refresh time by alot but we will work on away to work round that soon. Cleaned alot of player process
[b]Current features + updates:[/b] - Fully working Soulwars! - ClanWars red/white portal both work 100% - Dungoneering has been added just need to add rewards. - Jads attack has been fixed as before you could not pray out his attack due to the attack speed. - All Npc attack/health have been perfected to match current RS. - Pest control almost completed base - 85% [b]Grand exchange[/b] (Non-MySQL) without the lag! - [b]Cruciable[/b] minigame base has been started! Just need to find all the ID's
[b]Skills[/b] All skills work fine but still need fixing up. Skills such as farming are still under construction. Construction has not been started yet.
[b]Recent updates:[/b] Npc Updating Player updating Login Tabs Walking
